<doc f='exim/src/expand.c' l='7739'>/* These values are usually fixed boolean values, but they are permitted to be
expanded strings.

Arguments:
  addr       address being routed
  mtype      the module type
  mname      the module name
  dbg_opt    debug selectors
  oname      the option name
  bvalue     the router&apos;s boolean value
  svalue     the router&apos;s string value
  rvalue     where to put the returned value

Returns:     OK     value placed in rvalue
             DEFER  expansion failed
*/</doc>
